    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Katon)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 9</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 9</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 24 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 12 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 26</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H, F</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You raise a spire of lava to incinerate your enemies, making a touch attack against all targets in the area at a<br><br>+25 bonus. On hit, the attack deals 4d10 fire damage and causes targets to catch on fire unless they make a successful save.</p>\n\n\n\n",
